data.name: Tim Ho Wan Dim Sum Specialist
review_texts: It was a scrumptious late lunch we had today at this conveniently located branch in Cityplaza. It had been our fourth visit since its opening. As we chose to go there around 3 pm, we didn’t need to wait to be seated.
